🚀 How to Run the Secured Application
 Prerequisites

- Node.js (v16 or higher)
- npm (v8 or higher)

### Installation Steps

1. Clone the original Juice Shop
git clone https://github.com/juice-shop/juice-shop.git
2. Navigate to directory
cd juice-shop

3. Install dependencies
npm install

4. Install security packages
npm install helmet express-rate-limit isomorphic-dompurify winston

5. Start the application
npm start

6. Access the application


### Security Packages Installed

- **helmet** - Security headers (CSP, X-Frame-Options, etc.)
- **express-rate-limit** - Rate limiting for review submissions
- **isomorphic-dompurify** - XSS sanitization for user reviews
- **bcrypt** - Password hashing
- **validator** - Input validation
- **winston** - Security logging

